    "description": "✨Zombie GO is a puzzle turn-based game with more than 50 beautiful levels. You play as a man who survived the virus and must run away from zombies. On some levels, you must survive people.<br><br><br>💥With Zombie GO, you`ll experience:<br><br>🌟 Beautiful levels and environments<br>🌟 Hard and easy challenges and puzzles<br>🌟 Tools: Gun, Stone, Death Gear, Punch<br>🌟 Different types of enemies <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082290/extras/5ed332eb407a1c0cdebe44d2b1abfe7a.avif?t=1723646937\" width=650 height=106 /></span><br><br>For character movement, you should click on the nearest connected node to the node that the character is on! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082290/extras/7fbb7dae0208c35638f974caf9641f03.poster.avif?t=1723646937\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082290/extras/7fbb7dae0208c35638f974caf9641f03.webm?t=1723646937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082290/extras/7fbb7dae0208c35638f974caf9641f03.mp4?t=1723646937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can distract enemies by throwing stones at specific nodes. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082290/extras/3a66cbb0a001a4e00a3fc3dd49d25431.poster.avif?t=1723646937\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082290/extras/3a66cbb0a001a4e00a3fc3dd49d25431.webm?t=1723646937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082290/extras/3a66cbb0a001a4e00a3fc3dd49d25431.mp4?t=1723646937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can use Guns to kill enemies. Just remember each gun has just one bullet! After taking the gun you can click on each enemy that you want but you should be thinking about selecting the correct enemy!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082290/extras/333fec445bf483b1a8ed927c529ac955.poster.avif?t=1723646937\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082290/extras/333fec445bf483b1a8ed927c529ac955.webm?t=1723646937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082290/extras/333fec445bf483b1a8ed927c529ac955.mp4?t=1723646937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use the Keys to open doors! Blue Keys will open Blue Doors and Red Keys will open Red Doors.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082290/extras/a0578e7dbe8bc31674eced716e83a345.poster.avif?t=1723646937\" width=600 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082290/extras/a0578e7dbe8bc31674eced716e83a345.webm?t=1723646937\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082290/extras/a0578e7dbe8bc31674eced716e83a345.mp4?t=1723646937\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
